<p class="">The right hon. Gentleman is wrong in his recollection. The matter was not decided by the President of the Assembly, but by the Assembly itself, and, with great respect, I fail entirely to see how a body which is proceeding out of order can put itself into order by saying it is in order.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
