        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-3f3ab7ce-bfcb-49bf-baf9-e992a39d0f0f">
                Mr. Ernest Davies
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-3f3ab7ce-bfcb-49bf-baf9-e992a39d0f0f" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1950-11-13/debates/671ca015-daf9-4baa-bd7e-c29e5f67c8e1/CouncilOfEurope#contribution-3f3ab7ce-bfcb-49bf-baf9-e992a39d0f0f">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">I certainly do not agree that it was a waste of time to discuss the matter. I never made such a statement.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-3f3ab7ce-bfcb-49bf-baf9-e992a39d0f0f" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1950-11-13/debates/671ca015-daf9-4baa-bd7e-c29e5f67c8e1/CouncilOfEurope#contribution-3f3ab7ce-bfcb-49bf-baf9-e992a39d0f0f">
