<p class="">Would those powers include also that of calling on separate States for their quota of the armed forces of one kind and another, including finance?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-9c262bab-9d30-435d-a242-6daa643071ca" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
