                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">As I understand it, if His Majesty's Government could have taken part in the Schuman Plan negotiations without obligation, they would have been very willing to go.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-a09f6a79-48a8-469d-89c1-78bc8ea28e75" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1950-11-13/debates/671ca015-daf9-4baa-bd7e-c29e5f67c8e1/CouncilOfEurope#contribution-a09f6a79-48a8-469d-89c1-78bc8ea28e75">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-8c1db87a-6879-4adb-bb5a-e4ec0b150eea">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-8c1db87a-6879-4adb-bb5a-e4ec0b150eea">
