            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-e82b3398-c367-4d65-867d-729c9bf502e4" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
