<p class="">It was certainly carried, and if it was not unanimous there must have been an enormous majority.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-d3a2b9fc-c8aa-4072-a6c3-c1c95104c498" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
